#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.linalg.cholesky.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.linalg.cholesky"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.cholesky.cholesky:1 of
msgid "Cholesky decomposition."
msgstr "Cholesky 分解。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.cholesky.cholesky:3 of
msgid ""
"Return the Cholesky decomposition, `L * L.H`, of the square matrix `a`, "
"where `L` is lower-triangular and .H is the conjugate transpose operator "
"(which is the ordinary transpose if `a` is real-valued).  `a` must be "
"Hermitian (symmetric if real-valued) and positive-definite.  Only `L` is "
"actually returned."
msgstr ""
"返回方阵 `a` 的 Cholesky 分解 `L * L.H`，其中 `L` 是下三角矩阵，.H 是共轭"
"转置运算符（如果 `a` 是实数，则为普通转置）。`a` 必须是 Hermitian 矩阵（"
"如果是实数则是对称矩阵）且正定。只返回 `L`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.cholesky.cholesky of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.cholesky.cholesky:9 of
msgid ""
"Hermitian (symmetric if all elements are real), positive-definite input "
"matrix."
msgstr "Hermitian（如果所有元素都是实数则为对称）正定输入矩阵。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.cholesky.cholesky:12 of
msgid ""
"Whether to compute the upper or lower triangular Cholesky factorization."
"  Default is upper-triangular."
msgstr "是否计算上三角或下三角 Cholesky 分解。默认为上三角。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.cholesky.cholesky of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.cholesky.cholesky:16 of
msgid "**L** -- Upper or lower-triangular Cholesky factor of `a`."
msgstr "**L** -- `a` 的上三角或下三角 Cholesky 因子。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.cholesky.cholesky of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.cholesky.cholesky of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.cholesky.cholesky:19 of
msgid ""
"If the decomposition fails, for example, if `a` is not     positive-"
"definite."
msgstr "如果分解失败，例如 `a` 不是正定矩阵。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.cholesky.cholesky:22 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.cholesky.cholesky:23 of
msgid "Broadcasting rules apply, see the `mt.linalg` documentation for details."
msgstr "广播规则适用，请参阅 `mt.linalg` 文档了解详情。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.cholesky.cholesky:26 of
msgid "The Cholesky decomposition is often used as a fast way of solving"
msgstr "Cholesky 分解通常用于快速求解"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.cholesky.cholesky:28 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"A \\mathbf{x} = \\mathbf{b}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.cholesky.cholesky:30 of
msgid "(when `A` is both Hermitian/symmetric and positive-definite)."
msgstr "（当 `A` 既是 Hermitian/对称矩阵又是正定矩阵时）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.cholesky.cholesky:32 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid "First, we solve for :math:`\\mathbf{y}` in"
msgstr "首先，我们求解 :math:`\\mathbf{y}`，满足"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.cholesky.cholesky:34 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"L \\mathbf{y} = \\mathbf{b},\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.cholesky.cholesky:36 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid "and then for :math:`\\mathbf{x}` in"
msgstr "然后求解 :math:`\\mathbf{x}`，满足"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.cholesky.cholesky:38 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"L.H \\mathbf{x} = \\mathbf{y}.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

